narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Healthkeeperz, INC is a Durable Medical Equipment & Medical Supplies, Oxygen Equipment & Supplies provider based in Pembroke, NC. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $20.1M in Medicaid payments across 314K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $20.1M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
